1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 12=

26
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,400
Tingxiao.

27
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,120
Yuqing,

28
00:01:41,150 --> 00:01:42,150
you're finally back.

29
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:44,270
Dad, Uncle, Aunt,

30
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:45,150
and Aunties.

31
00:01:45,613 --> 00:01:46,980
(Lin Yuqing, cousin)
I was abroad.

32
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,870
The moment I got the news,
I rushed back.

33
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,886
I feel bad
about not seeing Uncle Youqiang

34
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,400
one last time.

35
00:01:56,710 --> 00:01:57,550
Zhi'er,

36
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,760
please stay strong.

37
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,350
Yuqing, your timing is perfect.

38
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,070
The lawyer just said

39
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:07,430
this girl will inherit everything.

40
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:10,430
You've given so much to Linhai Group.

41
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:12,030
Shouldn't you get some shares too?

42
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,280
Exactly, Yuqing.

43
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:15,470
We elders can't just watch this.

44
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,680
Tell us what to do.

45
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,796
Just say the word,

46
00:02:17,807 --> 00:02:18,859
and we'll follow your lead.

47
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:19,710
- Right.
- Yes.

48
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,190
Everyone, listen to me.

49
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:23,150
The media is waiting outside.

50
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,960
If we keep making a scene,

51
00:02:25,190 --> 00:02:26,430
we'll be the laughingstock

52
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:27,710
of the whole city.

53
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,776
But we can't just let
an illegitimate daughter

54
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,139
who's married out control

55
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:33,000
the Group.

56
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,240
Uncle,

57
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:36,870
Zhi'er is now
Uncle Youqiang's only child.

58
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,400
Inheriting his personal assets
is lawful.

59
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:41,840
Of course,

60
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:44,240
Linhai Group doesn't belong
to one person.

61
00:02:44,710 --> 00:02:46,120
It belongs to everyone here.

62
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,470
The company needs stability now.

63
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,750
I trust Zhi'er's abilities.

64
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,200
However,

65
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,630
the choice of the new CEO

66
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,520
should be decided by the board.

67
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,840
I think Yuqing makes a good point.

68
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,030
Let's do it Yuqing's way.

69
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:04,310
Alright.

70
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,190
Zhi'er, please,

71
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,560
come by the company tomorrow.

72
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,200
Sure.

73
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,680
Tingxiao,

74
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,710
long time no see.

75
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,910
(What a smart tactical retreat.)

76
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:25,190
(But I'm not that easy to handle.)

77
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,030
(For Lin Zhi'er)

78
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:28,730
(and the investigation,)

79
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,360
(the Group)

80
00:03:31,030 --> 00:03:32,150
(will be mine.)

81
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:19,040
Honestly, it doesn't matter
if Zhi'er comes.

82
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,040
The company has us here.

83
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,600
With Yuqing here,

84
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,560
everything will run smoothly.

85
00:05:27,830 --> 00:05:28,920
With Yuqing here,

86
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:31,009
of course, I feel at ease.

87
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,760
But I am

88
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,240
the largest shareholder

89
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,630
and the new CEO.

90
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,840
How can I not come?

91
00:05:37,410 --> 00:05:38,290
Zhi'er,

92
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:39,430
you still don't get it.

93
00:05:39,630 --> 00:05:40,510
We're saying

94
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:43,480
we need a CEO who's highly capable

95
00:05:43,630 --> 00:05:45,040
and experienced

96
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,070
and can lead us to win.

97
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,680
Not an unqualified

98
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:50,160
and uneducated housewife.

99
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,080
Don't say that.

100
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:56,190
Whoever becomes the CEO

101
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:57,310
will work for the Group.

102
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:58,870
I also believe

103
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:00,190
that whoever takes over

104
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,680
won't affect our bond.

105
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:03,670
Right?

106
00:06:04,310 --> 00:06:05,150
Of course.

107
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,480
A disguised trap is also beneficial.

108
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:09,390
Thanks, Yuqing.

109
00:06:11,950 --> 00:06:12,800
Wang Dajun,

110
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,750
you've been quite aggressive.

111
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,310
Was your debt cleared?

112
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,040
Last March,

113
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,830
you got a huge gambling debt,

114
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:25,950
so you raised the budget

115
00:06:26,390 --> 00:06:28,070
for the South City project
by 30 million.

116
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:30,560
It ended up in your personal account,

117
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,640
right?

118
00:06:33,173 --> 00:06:34,510
You can't smear me without proof.

119
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,440
Mr. Jia,

120
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:38,390
your son skipped the bidding process

121
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:40,750
and took our new company's renovation

122
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:43,630
at three times the market rate.

123
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,640
You...

124
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,750
Don't make things up.

125
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,310
You get what you pay for.

126
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,433
I spent every cent where it mattered.

127
00:06:49,606 --> 00:06:51,192
Check the books if you don't believe me.

128
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:53,120
Then, everyone, take a look

129
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,430
at these cooked books.

130
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,950
Let's see what happened.

131
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,520
Zhi'er,

132
00:07:01,750 --> 00:07:03,360
they've contributed to the Group.

133
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:04,950
Let's talk it through.

134
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:07,070
I am talking this through.

135
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,830
If I weren't holding back,

136
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:10,000
would everyone here

137
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:12,160
still be sitting here just fine?

138
00:07:20,559 --> 00:07:21,619
Tomorrow, you have to deal

139
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:23,560
(The night before)
with those shareholders.

140
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:24,880
What's your plan?

141
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:27,590
Look.

142
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:33,800
So much evidence.

143
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:35,920
How did you get it all?

144
00:07:37,070 --> 00:07:37,910
Mr. Lu,

145
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:40,240
I'm Jin Chanchan, after all.

146
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:43,790
Alright.

147
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,800
So, the evidence

148
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,560
I prepared won't be needed.

149
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:51,670
It's mine now.

150
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,680
When this is over,

151
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,120
I'll deal with these leeches one by one.

152
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:04,390
Every one of you...

153
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:06,800
Sticky fingers

154
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:08,390
and two-faced traitors,

155
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:13,310
you'd better watch yourselves.

156
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,950
Can we now

157
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,430
have a calm talk?

158
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:26,960
Zhi'er,

159
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:29,600
it's necessary to sort out
the company discipline.

160
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:31,270
But

161
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,200
running a company isn't child's play.

162
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,150
You're inexperienced.

163
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:37,320
The company's real problem is this:

164
00:08:37,466 --> 00:08:39,036
The Lianxin Island project was delayed,

165
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,480
leaving a huge funding gap.

166
00:08:41,550 --> 00:08:42,750
Just tightening discipline

167
00:08:43,670 --> 00:08:45,000
won't solve that.

168
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:47,960
You really nailed it.

169
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,840
Under your brilliant leadership,

170
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:54,270
the Group was heading for disaster.

171
00:08:54,790 --> 00:08:55,750
Now, I can secure

172
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:58,790
2 billion from Luzhou Group.

173
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:01,360
Does that count as helping Linhai?

174
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:02,510
2 billion?

175
00:09:02,630 --> 00:09:03,550
2 billion?

176
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,510
Luzhou Group can barely save itself.

177
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:07,510
How could it give us 2 billion?

178
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,670
Who says it can't?

179
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:16,840
Tingxiao.

180
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,960
Luzhou Group's 2 billion is ready.

181
00:09:25,630 --> 00:09:27,056
The agreement can be signed anytime.

182
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,630
Even with new funding, so what?

183
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,360
Lianxin Island is shut down now.

184
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,000
We're losing over ten million a day.

185
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:39,319
How are you going to fix that?

186
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:41,960
Everyone, don't worry.

187
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,190
The shutdown issue

188
00:09:43,201 --> 00:09:44,967
has been handled
by Chairman Lu and Mr. Lu.

189
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,200
Lianxin Island can resume work anytime.

190
00:09:54,750 --> 00:09:55,590
Resume work?

191
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:56,580
(Approval of Resume)

192
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,870
Dad, how did you pull that off?

193
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:01,320
Thanks to Lin Youqiang.

194
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,750
He drew
the investigation team's focus away

195
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,440
and bought me time.

196
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,270
Once the fine is paid,

197
00:10:08,150 --> 00:10:10,000
the project can be restarted.

198
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:13,000
It was just a fine?

199
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:14,390
Of course not.

200
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:16,390
We had to smooth things over.

201
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:18,360
But that cost

202
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,960
is barely worth mentioning

203
00:10:20,971 --> 00:10:22,217
compared to the future benefit.

204
00:10:25,550 --> 00:10:26,840
Lianxin Island is back on track.

205
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,286
You're not happy about it?

206
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,560
Of course, I am.

207
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,750
I'm just thinking about our next move.

208
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:34,990
Good.

209
00:10:35,030 --> 00:10:35,870
Easy.

210
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,160
In a bit,

211
00:10:37,510 --> 00:10:38,600
take this with you

212
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:40,630
and go to Linhai Group.

213
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:49,390
On behalf of Luzhou Group,

214
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,150
I fully support Lin Zhi'er

215
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:53,750
as the new CEO.

216
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:55,920
Any objections?

217
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:07,510
Then, congrats to Zhi'er
on becoming the CEO.

218
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,000
(The real battle)

219
00:11:28,910 --> 00:11:30,320
(is only just beginning.)

220
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,440
You're finally here.

221
00:11:41,460 --> 00:11:42,330
How are you feeling?

222
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,870
You'll give the speech as the CEO.

223
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:44,870
Are you nervous?

224
00:11:46,270 --> 00:11:47,200
Why would I be nervous?

225
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:48,630
Others are the ones

226
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:49,870
who should be nervous.

227
00:11:51,150 --> 00:11:52,440
You're really composed.

228
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,320
I worried for nothing.

229
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,290
Come on.

230
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,390
I'll introduce you to key partners.

231
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:02,720
How clumsy.

232
00:12:03,079 --> 00:12:04,148
Can you take responsibility

233
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:05,299
for ruining Ms. Lin's image?

234
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,200
I'm sorry.

235
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:07,710
It's okay.

236
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,080
I'm sorry.

237
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:12,510
Zhi'er, I'm really sorry.

238
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,240
Sorry for the poor planning.

239
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:16,480
You can't wear these shoes now.

240
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:18,750
I have a new limited-edition pair
in my car.

241
00:12:18,899 --> 00:12:19,859
I haven't worn them yet.

242
00:12:19,953 --> 00:12:20,986
We're about the same size.

243
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,600
I'll have someone bring them over.

244
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:24,470
No need.

245
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:27,120
You're the new CEO.

246
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,360
Everything you do

247
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:29,790
reflects the Group's image.

248
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,790
Everyone will be watching soon.

249
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:34,390
You can't debut in dirty shoes.

250
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,080
Alright then.

251
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:37,990
Thank you.

252
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,270
Why be so formal with me?

253
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:40,350
We're cousins.

254
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:41,840
We should look out for each other.

255
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,920
How are they?

256
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:50,230
They look great.

257
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:55,870
Distinguished guests,

258
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:57,440
please join me in a warm welcome

259
00:12:57,750 --> 00:12:59,840
for Linhai Group's new CEO,

260
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:02,270
Ms. Lin Zhi'er, to the stage.

261
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,280
This...

262
00:13:27,612 --> 00:13:30,005
They said taking over Linhai Group
would be full of traps.

263
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:31,240
And on Day 1,

264
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:33,000
I met someone blocking my way.

265
00:13:33,630 --> 00:13:35,240
Are these shoes meant

266
00:13:35,790 --> 00:13:37,030
to tell me to back off?

267
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,120
I won't.

268
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,600
I'll just toss them out.

269
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,840
Barefoot fears no one in shoes.

270
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,390
As Linhai Group's new CEO,

271
00:13:51,270 --> 00:13:53,510
I'll give this my all

272
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,030
and stand with everyone

273
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:57,840
against every challenge ahead.

274
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:02,670
With all employees united,

275
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:03,800
Linhai Group

276
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:05,630
will move toward a brighter future.

277
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,570
♪This door♪

278
00:14:33,970 --> 00:14:38,720
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

279
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:42,760
♪With a voice even lighter♪

280
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:45,570
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

281
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:47,390
♪I know now♪

282
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:52,600
♪What the chill in my body means♪

283
00:14:52,950 --> 00:14:55,820
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

284
00:14:56,020 --> 00:14:59,440
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

285
00:14:59,610 --> 00:15:02,600
♪To complete♪

286
00:15:03,060 --> 00:15:06,810
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

287
00:15:06,950 --> 00:15:09,450
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

288
00:15:09,590 --> 00:15:13,140
♪Like a door with no key♪

289
00:15:13,450 --> 00:15:15,770
